Here are the details of commercial rooms in Calia
* denotes shop code was partially adapted from another Domain's sources

Name: bakery   Location: Gelan   Coder(s):  Maniac*      
Path:   ~Calia/gelan/rooms/bakery.c
Details: Sells various pastry based foods, wide range of food values. 
         Food items stocked in ~Calia/gelan/objects.
         Npc: ~Calia/gelan/monsters/baker.c


Name: grocery   Location: Gelan   Coder(s): Maniac
Path: ~Calia/gelan/rooms/grocery.c
Details: Sells special food (fruit and veg) that can recuperate small amounts
         of mana/fatigue/hp in the player who eats it. The fruit is in
         ~Calia/gelan/objects. The inheritable fruit code, and doc, is in
         ~Calia/std.


Name: bank     Location: Palace  Coder(s):  Glykron     
Path: ~Calia/palace/rooms/light/bank.c
Bank ID: NONE (not in use)
Details: Ordinary vanilla bank  


Name: bank  Location: Gelan    Coder(s):  Glykron/Maniac  
Path: ~Calia/gelan/rooms/bank.c
Bank ID: Gnomes of Genesis Bank ID = 1401
Details: Enhanced bank (for npc banker) plus gnome money deposit. Also
         there's a small quest at this site (see ~Calia/private/QUESTS). 
         Npc: ~Calia/gelan/monsters/ska.c


Name: blacksmith   Location: Gelan   Coder(s) Maniac*         
Path: ~Calia/gelan/rooms/blacksmith.c
Details: Major revision of Gondor blacksmith code including forging polearms,
         now resides in the npc code, ~Calia/gelan/monsters/bubba.c 


Name: hairdresser  Location: Gelan  Coder(s) Glykron/Maniac 
Path: ~Calia/gelan/rooms/hairdresser.c,
Details: Sells haircuts, where player gets a hair shadow that displays
         hair of the chosen style, and a cmdsoul that gives some hair 
         emotes (both are found in ~Calia/gelan/specials). 
         Also sells "eye washes", eye shadow similar in principle 
         to the hair shadow. These are found in ~Calia/gelan/specials. 
         Npc: ~Calia/gelan/monsters/bigoudi.c


Name: inn  Location: Gelan  Coder(s) Deinonychus*    
Path: ~Calia/gelan/rooms/inn.c
Details: Sells alco in "bottles" of various sizes (see 
         ~Calia/gelan/objects)  
         Npc: ~Calia/gelan/monsters/orgulas.c
         

Name: shop   Location: Palace   Coder(s):  Glykron         
Path: ~Calia/palace/rooms/light/shop.c
Details: Ordinary vanilla shop.


Name: shop   Location: Palace   Coder(s):  Maniac*   
Path: ~Calia/palace/rooms/light/hardware_shop.c
Details: Sells backpacks and sacks, torches, rope, and a couple of quest
         items (cloth and chisels).


Name: shop   Location: Gelan   Coder(s):  Maniac*         
Path: ~Calia/gelan/rooms/shop.c
Details: Enhanced shop (Npc, found in ~Calia/gelan/monsters/coiney.c).


Name: tattoo parlour  Location: Gelan  Coder(s): Stexx/Digit     
Path: ~Calia/gelan/rooms/t_par.c          
Details: Tattoo shop connected to the hairdresser, has a big range
         of tattoos that players can purchase, with flexibility (players  
         can select from a range of adjectives to go in the tattoo 
         description). Most of the code is in ~Calia/gelan/tattoos.
         Npc code is in ~Calia/gelan/monsters/budda.c


Name: fish market   Location: seaside village    Coder(s): Maniac & Jaacar
Path: ~Calia/sea/beach/village8.c
Details: A shop that deals only in fish caught in the local sea,  
         they pay special prices for them and sell them on for a profit. 
Npc: ~Calia/sea/creatures/mar_iella.c 


Name: The Leaping Dolphin (pub)  Location: seaside vilage   
Coder(s) Maniac & Jaacar
Path:  ~Calia/sea/beach/village2.c
Details: A simple pub, sells some simple food and drinks. 
Npc: ~Calia/sea/creatures/bier_nut.c 


Name: kroug shop    Location: cave near beach    Coder(s): Maniac & Jaacar
Path: ~Calia/sea/beach/sea_cave.c 
Details: A `secret' shop for evil players to sell the stuff they loot from 
         the villagers. 
Npc: ~Calia/sea/creatures/ripper.c  

Name: Thalassian Shop  Location: Thalassia    Coder(s): Jaacar
Path: ~Calia/sea/thalassia/major/shop.c
Details: An underwater shop in the city of Thalassia.
Npc: none

Name: Thalassian Blacksmith   Location: Thalassia    Coder(s): Jaacar & Sarr
Path: ~Calia/sea/thalassia/major/smith.c
Details: A basic smithy that allows player to sharpen/wax weapons and 
         Mend armours (not broken ones).
Npc: ~Calia/sea/creatures/smithy.c

Name: Thalassian Bank   Location: Thalassia    Coder(s): Jaacar
Path: ~Calia/sea/thalassia/lesser/bank.c
Bank ID: Gnomes of Genesis Bank ID = 1402
Details: Unknown

Name: Thalassian Hospital    Location: Thalassia    Coder(s): Jaacar
Path: ~Calia/sea/thalassia/lesser/hospital.c
Details: The hospital gives players a chance to remove those ugly scars
         That they have gotten from getting killed.
Npc: none

Name: Royal Bank of Argos   Location: Argos
Path: ~Calia/argos/metro/rooms/bank.c
Bank ID: Gnomes of Genesis Bank ID = 1403
Details: Unknown

Name: Elemental Temple Bank   Location: Elemental Temple
Path: ~Calia/guilds/elementalists/temple/bank.c
Bank ID: Gnomes of Genesis Bank ID = 1404
Details: The Elemental Temple is the guild home of the Elemental Clerics,
         Worshippers, and Seekers.

shop(outdoor)   Zima            ~zima/argos/nwterr/tentcourt.c
pub/inn         Zima            ~zima/argos/nwterr/tentinn.c

